@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Me";
}

<section class="page-hero">
    <div class="section-heading">
        <p data-i18n-en="About me" data-i18n-vi="Gioi thieu">About me</p>
        <h2 data-i18n-en="The page where you explain who you are, how you work, and what kind of builder you are." data-i18n-vi="Trang de ban gioi thieu ban than, cach ban lam viec va phong cach xay dung san pham cua minh.">The page where you explain who you are, how you work, and what kind of builder you are.</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="page-lead" data-i18n-en="Replace this copy with your real story: your background, your technical strengths, what you care about in product work, and the kind of clients or teams you want to work with." data-i18n-vi="Hay thay noi dung nay bang cau chuyen that cua ban: nen tang, diem manh ky thuat, dieu ban quan tam trong cong viec san pham, va nhung khach hang hoac doi ngu ma ban muon hop tac.">Replace this copy with your real story: your background, your technical strengths, what you care about in product work, and the kind of clients or teams you want to work with.</p>
</section>

<section class="section-shell about-shell">
    <div class="about-copy">
        <p data-i18n-en="Profile" data-i18n-vi="Ho so">Profile</p>
        <h2 data-i18n-en="Product-minded, detail-focused, and comfortable moving from concept into implementation." data-i18n-vi="Tu duy san pham, chu trong chi tiet va thoai mai di tu y tuong den trien khai thuc te.">Product-minded, detail-focused, and comfortable moving from concept into implementation.</h2>
        <p data-i18n-en="Use this section to describe your experience in a more human way. Talk about how you think, how you approach web apps, and what separates your work from generic template-based delivery." data-i18n-vi="Su dung phan nay de mo ta kinh nghiem cua ban mot cach gan gui hon. Hay noi ve cach ban tu duy, cach ban tiep can web app, va dieu gi khien cong viec cua ban khac voi nhung mau template chung chung.">Use this section to describe your experience in a more human way. Talk about how you think, how you approach web apps, and what separates your work from generic template-based delivery.</p>
    </div>
    <aside class="about-note">
        <h3 data-i18n-en="Strengths" data-i18n-vi="Diem manh">Strengths</h3>
        <ul>
            <li data-i18n-en="Interface design and frontend structure" data-i18n-vi="Thiet ke giao dien va cau truc frontend">Interface design and frontend structure</li>
            <li data-i18n-en="Responsive layout and visual refinement" data-i18n-vi="Bo cuc responsive va tinh chinh hinh anh">Responsive layout and visual refinement</li>
            <li data-i18n-en="ASP.NET Core, Razor Pages, and practical delivery" data-i18n-vi="ASP.NET Core, Razor Pages va kha nang trien khai thuc te">ASP.NET Core, Razor Pages, and practical delivery</li>
            <li data-i18n-en="Clear communication and structured execution" data-i18n-vi="Giao tiep ro rang va trien khai co cau truc">Clear communication and structured execution</li>
        </ul>
    </aside>
</section>

<section class="section-shell">
    <div class="section-heading">
        <p data-i18n-en="Approach" data-i18n-vi="Cach tiep can">Approach</p>
        <h2 data-i18n-en="How you can frame the way you work." data-i18n-vi="Cach ban co the trinh bay phuong phap lam viec cua minh.">How you can frame the way you work.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="service-grid">
        <article>
            <h3 data-i18n-en="Understand the goal" data-i18n-vi="Hieu ro muc tieu">Understand the goal</h3>
            <p data-i18n-en="Start with audience, constraints, and the exact job the page or product needs to do." data-i18n-vi="Bat dau tu doi tuong nguoi dung, cac rang buoc va nhiem vu cu the ma trang web hoac san pham can giai quyet.">Start with audience, constraints, and the exact job the page or product needs to do.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h3 data-i18n-en="Design with intention" data-i18n-vi="Thiet ke co chu dich">Design with intention</h3>
            <p data-i18n-en="Focus on hierarchy, pacing, content clarity, and interface consistency instead of decoration alone." data-i18n-vi="Tap trung vao thu bac thong tin, nhip dieu, do ro rang cua noi dung va su nhat quan cua giao dien thay vi chi trang tri.">Focus on hierarchy, pacing, content clarity, and interface consistency instead of decoration alone.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h3 data-i18n-en="Build cleanly" data-i18n-vi="Xay dung gon gang">Build cleanly</h3>
            <p data-i18n-en="Translate the design into maintainable structure and styling that holds up beyond the first release." data-i18n-vi="Chuyen hoa thiet ke thanh cau truc va CSS de bao tri, van on dinh sau khi ra mat phien ban dau tien.">Translate the design into maintainable structure and styling that holds up beyond the first release.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h3 data-i18n-en="Refine the details" data-i18n-vi="Chinh sua chi tiet">Refine the details</h3>
            <p data-i18n-en="Polish spacing, responsiveness, and interaction quality so the result feels deliberate and finished." data-i18n-vi="Tinh chinh khoang cach, responsive va chat luong tuong tac de ket qua cuoi cung co cam giac chau chu va hoan thien.">Polish spacing, responsiveness, and interaction quality so the result feels deliberate and finished.</p>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>
